PrecisRegulations Amending the NAFTA RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS to the extent of updating tariff item numbers and references to re-numbered provisions in the Customs Act and by removing temporary rules of origin that have expired, in order to ensure that trade under NAFTA is subject to a uniform system of tariff item numbering and product descriptions.
